orbitdeck (0.35.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix the Windows standalone build crashing at launch with "DLL load failed
    while importing ft2font": bundle matplotlib's native extensions and its
    vendored FreeType DLLs (collect_all + the matplotlib.libs directory), and the
    same for numpy/PIL. Startup errors now show a Tk dialog instead of a cryptic
    secondary "NoneType has no attribute write" traceback.

 -- Paul Stoetzer, N8HM <noreply@example.com>  Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

orbitdeck (0.35.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix OSCARLOCATOR simulator arc dragging: the dragged arc no longer leaves a
    ghost copy on the map, and the drag is smooth (removed the fragile blitting
    fast-path; throttle motion events instead). Add equator-crossing-longitude
    and minutes-after-crossing sliders to the Sweep panel, alongside dragging.

 -- Paul Stoetzer, N8HM <noreply@example.com>  Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

orbitdeck (0.35.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

